1. ** Questions **
If you have some questions first read FAQ, 
second ask in smbc mailing list smbc@airm.net.

2. ** Recomended **
- Samba 2.8.8 or later. Advised samba version is the latest version. 
  (Samba must be compiled with smbclient library.)
- Ncurses library.
- popt library from http://www.gnu.org/directory/libs/popt.html
- and others

3. ** Documentation **
http://smbc.airm.net/manual/

4. Example configuration for polish.

add to file smb.conf below lines
unix charset = ISO8859-2
display charset = ISO8859-2

set environment variable LANG as
export LANG=pl_PL
